<br />
<font size="3">CONGRATULATIONS TO KAIDMAN FROM <b>MAELIN STARPYRE</b> FOR BEING THE FIRST SERVERWIDE to get 2.0!!!!!<br />
<br />
And HUGE THANKS TO ALL CONTRIBUTORS. ESPECIALLY to <br />
<b>saryrn.KRYTTOS</b> (that got us unstuck)<br />
<b>rathe.KINAKI </b>(thanks a lot bro - huge info)<br />
<b>prexus.MOLILYA</b> (also huuuge info, thanks bro)<br />
